Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.00,0:00:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在为谁而歌唱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.90,0:00:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随着音符的跳动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.70,0:00:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心情会慢慢消沉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音乐是为谁而存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.90,0:00:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是一直以来的那种声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.50,0:00:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.60,0:00:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是什么怨女的幽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.20,0:00:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事的 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.50,0:01:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直在你身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.30,0:01:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你啊 明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.70,0:01:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日你好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.40,0:01:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.30,0:03:29.55,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}吉他和梦想和歌唱老师的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.40,0:03:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.00,0:03:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我跟你对一下作业答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.30,0:03:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要 我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.60,0:03:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了 明日 谢谢你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.40,0:03:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日什么都会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.60,0:03:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是 就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.20,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本没什么不擅长的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种感觉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.20,0:04:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.10,0:04:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 像我就算术不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有不擅长的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愉快的音乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.70,0:04:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是个大音痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.20,0:04:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 现在开始唱歌考试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.80,0:04:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.90,0:04:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs20}春天的小河涓涓流淌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.90,0:04:48.10,extrajp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}春の小川はさらさら行くよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.60,0:04:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs20}岸边的紫罗兰和莲花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.60,0:04:56.80,extrajp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}岸のすみれや れんげの花に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.80,0:04:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好紧张啊 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.20,0:05:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs20}幽雅的姿态 绚丽的色彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.20,0:05:05.60,extrajp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}すがたやさしく　色うつくしく
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.30,0:05:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}明日是最后一号 考试要到下周
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}没事吧 你脸色很不好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.10,0:05:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs20}盛开吧 小河如是轻声诉说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.10,0:05:14.30,extrajp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}咲けよ咲けよと　ささやきながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}没事的 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.20,0:05:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}我好期待明日唱歌啊 一定唱得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没这回事 我是音痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 下一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.70,0:05:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是像这样的人才会唱得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.40,0:05:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 明日就是这种感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.90,0:05:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我真的是音痴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.90,0:05:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.30,0:05:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1400)}岸边的紫罗兰和莲花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.90,0:05:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,386)}被大家这么期待了该如何是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.00,0:05:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始一周 我要每天练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.10,0:06:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春天…的…小河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走调走得厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.90,0:06:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岸边的紫罗兰和莲花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.70,0:06:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的歌声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.60,0:06:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽雅的姿态 绚丽的色彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.80,0:06:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面谁在唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.90,0:06:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盛开吧 小河如是轻声诉说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.40,0:06:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的人 是男生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 是隔壁的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.60,0:06:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.30,0:06:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 您唱得真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.20,0:06:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我想成为歌手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌手吗 真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.60,0:07:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连出道都没 试音总是失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.60,0:07:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 但是真的很好听啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是超级音痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有客人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.20,0:07:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正男 在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.70,0:07:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微走开一下 你等我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.60,0:07:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正男先生 原来是男的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.90,0:07:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.90,0:07:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.20,0:07:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我带了慰问品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.20,0:07:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.10,0:07:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.30,0:07:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正男君 我做了便当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.20,0:07:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.40,0:08:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很期待你的现场演出啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还会再来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.00,0:08:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.30,0:08:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正男君 我知道这会给你添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.60,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害 是你的朋友吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实也不是很熟的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.10,0:08:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她们都说我的歌很好听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.40,0:08:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚我听到说很期待你的现场演唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里唱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前在音乐秀场唱过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.10,0:09:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没钱 舞台费就拿不出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连这里的房租都危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.70,0:09:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想着还是回老家去算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了这些热心人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.10,0:09:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就不愁吃了 心想就这样过下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.10,0:09:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想唱的时候半夜也能唱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.40,0:09:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那半夜微微的歌声原来是他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.00,0:09:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我叫一之仓正男 你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫山田明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.20,0:09:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你的歌很好听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.90,0:09:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.80,0:09:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你的歌很好听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我一直练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.60,0:09:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能像他那样唱得那么好听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.60,0:10:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日 明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.20,0:10:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是那个声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.40,0:10:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细听啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.80,0:10:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好动听的歌声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.80,0:10:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我早点发现就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.60,0:10:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 真是动听的歌声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.80,0:10:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 晚上好 是不是太吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 您唱得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是明日的姐姐 山田今日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像变冷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天看来只能到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.10,0:11:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
