Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点回家练习唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.00,0:11:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能唱得像一之仓先生那样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.00,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是一之仓先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.80,0:11:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.30,0:11:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 明日 你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.50,0:12:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正要回去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.60,0:12:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我正准备回家练习唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.20,0:12:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 如果可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.30,0:12:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能教我唱歌呢 拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.30,0:12:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我学校有歌唱考试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.90,0:12:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没有谢礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.70,0:12:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不行的话也无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.20,0:12:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.80,0:12:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.30,0:12:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么快点开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么能够发声的东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,口琴键盘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.30,0:12:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就跟唱我吹出的音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.80,0:13:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do…re…mi
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.20,0:13:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 fa和la好像发不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是姐姐以前用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.80,0:13:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和妈妈讲让她帮你买新的不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.50,0:13:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家没有妈妈 也没有爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.70,0:13:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就你们俩住在那个公寓里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我什么都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.20,0:13:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我有姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.70,0:13:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 如果有什么我能帮忙的尽管开口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.60,0:13:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你都已经在教我唱歌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.50,0:14:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我想听一之仓先生唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.60,0:14:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上 随时都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.60,0:14:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要大声唱准音调
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(80,295)}锻炼肌肉计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(80,325)}腹肌练习 30次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(80,355)}举臂练习 30次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.30,0:14:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是要运用全身肌肉的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.30,0:14:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.20,0:14:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这以后每天一之仓先生都教我唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.80,0:14:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,25 26
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.10,0:15:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}春天的小河涓涓流淌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.80,0:15:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}岸边的紫罗兰和莲花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.60,0:15:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}幽雅的姿态 绚丽的色彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.20,0:15:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}盛开吧 小河如是轻声诉说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.90,0:15:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日 真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.40,0:15:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么唱得这么好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师教得好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日真棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.90,0:16:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快去跟一之仓先生汇报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.40,0:16:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.00,0:16:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之仓先生 我考试考得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.20,0:16:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是不在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 马上会回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.50,0:16:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没回来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.70,0:16:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后经过了一周一之仓先生也没有回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.00,0:16:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之仓先生怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.00,0:17:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正男 正男 你在的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.40,0:17:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.10,0:17:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.70,0:17:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你们是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.70,0:17:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是他邻居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.90,0:17:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之仓先生已有一星期没回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们知道什么的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.50,0:17:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.80,0:17:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实他好像试音成功了却没去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.00,0:17:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明私下里这么努力练习了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.10,0:17:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还听说他把他心爱的吉他都卖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.90,0:17:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉他是比正男生命更重要的宝物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.20,0:17:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然那个是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么高兴地教我唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.40,0:17:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明唱得那么好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想听一之仓先生唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 包在我身上 随时都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们约定好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.70,0:18:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说了到时候再唱给我听的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.20,0:18:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飒飒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.50,0:18:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有歌声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缓缓地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.40,0:18:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,微风吹拂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.40,0:18:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.10,0:18:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.50,0:18:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 正男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.10,0:18:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让人担心死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.90,0:18:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正男君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.80,0:18:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去附近打工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像给你们添了不少麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.80,0:19:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次可千万要通知我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.90,0:19:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很喜欢一之仓先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为总是试音失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.70,0:19:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心想再这样下去也是徒劳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.70,0:19:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还想过放弃唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.20,0:19:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我现在想继续唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.60,0:19:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我去打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后把这把吉他买回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.20,0:19:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.70,0:19:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟一个人约定好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.40,0:19:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次还要唱歌给她听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.30,0:20:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飒飒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.60,0:20:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缓缓地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.50,0:20:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要继续歌唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.10,0:20:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我唯一能做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.60,0:20:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,微风轻拂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.60,0:20:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌声真是奇妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随着音符的跳动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.50,0:20:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心慢慢温暖起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.70,0:20:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我会唱下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.90,0:20:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.40,0:20:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纷纷扬扬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.10,0:21:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和煦阳光是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.10,0:21:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 为了能够一直留在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要和姐姐一起努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了一直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.50,0:21:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够听到歌声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.40,0:22:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日抽签抽到的手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.60,0:23:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以好好珍惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.10,0:23:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐为什么不接啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.20,0:23:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贫穷姐妹物语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.90,0:23:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,思念和不安和手机的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬请观看
